<text top="704" left="122" width="252" height="14" font="1">The situation in Bosnia and Herzegovina</text>
<text top="740" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Letter dated 7 March 1997 from the Secretary-General addressed to the President of the Security Council</text>
